  "about": {
    "title": "About MOBA Wiki",
    "subtitle": "A free, community-driven reference for Mobile Legends: Bang Bang players.",
    "whatTitle": "What is MOBA Wiki?",
    "whatP1": "MOBA Wiki is an independent, fan-made database and guide site focused on Mobile Legends: Bang Bang. Our goal is to give every player — from beginners to veterans — fast, accurate, and well-organized information about heroes, items, abilities, and the ever-changing meta.",
    "whatP2": "We built this site because we were frustrated with scattered information: patch notes on one site, tier lists on another, hero builds in random Discord servers. MOBA Wiki brings everything together in one place, updated regularly, and completely free.",
    "featuresTitle": "What You'll Find Here",
    "f1Title": "Hero Database",
    "f1Desc": "Detailed pages for every hero — base stats, ability descriptions with level-by-level values, recommended builds, lore, and roles. Data is sourced from official game APIs and kept up to date after every patch.",
    "f2Title": "Tier Lists & Win Rates",
    "f2Desc": "Hero rankings based on real match data, broken down by rank tier. Our tier list updates regularly to reflect the current meta — not someone's personal opinion.",
    "f3Title": "Counter Pick Guide",
    "f3Desc": "Find the best heroes to counter any matchup. Understand which heroes struggle against whom and make smarter picks.",
    "f4Title": "Item Database",
    "f4Desc": "Full item database with stats, effects, and build paths — searchable and filterable by type, stat, and use case.",
    "f5Title": "Patch Notes History",
